OL,3,CThousands of veterans thought to be
OL,4,Caffected by faulty earplugs
OL,6,FWords by ITV News Producer Cat Dinneny
OL,8,FTens of thousands of British military
OL,9,Fpersonnel could have suffered hearing
OL,10,Floss or damage as a result of faulty
OL,11,Fear defenders.
OL,13,FAmerican firm 3M supplied at least
OL,14,F400,000 sets of its Combat Arms
OL,15,FEarplugs to the Ministry of Defence
OL,16,Fover a 20-year period, but it's
OL,17,Falleged they were defective.
OL,19,FThe company is now being sued in the
OL,20,FUK after settling a $6 billion lawsuit
OL,21,Fin the US for similar allegations.
