OL,4,Caffected by faulty earplugs
OL,6,FTom Longstaff, a partner at KP Law,
OL,7,Fwhich is launching the class action,
OL,8,Fsaid: "3M will have known its earplugs
OL,9,Fwere defective while still supplying
OL,10,Fthem to the UK military. It is only
OL,11,Fright that the men and women whose
OL,12,Flives have been impacted receive
OL,13,Fjustice and compensation."
OL,15,FThe ear defenders were commonly used
OL,16,Fin the military between 2003 and 2023.
