OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News, Mr Longstaff
OL,7,Fsaid: "It suffered from a design
OL,8,Fdefect which meant the product wasn't
OL,9,Ffit for purpose and didn't protect
OL,10,Fmembers of the Armed Forces against
OL,11,Fvery loud levels of noise to which
OL,12,Fthey were exposed."
OL,14,FIt's estimated tens of thousands of
OL,15,Fveterans and servicemen and women have
OL,16,Fexperienced hearing loss, tinnitus and
OL,17,Frelated issues, including stress,
OL,18,Fanxiety and depression as a result of
OL,19,Fusing them.
