OL,6,FAdam Stone served as a Corporal in the
OL,7,FRoyal Marines between 2003 and 2012,
OL,8,Fincluding a tour of Iraq. He has
OL,9,Fhearing loss in his left ear and said
OL,10,Fhe regularly used the 3M ear defenders.
OL,12,FHe told ITV News: "Depending on the
OL,13,Fsetting, it was far easier to wear the
OL,14,Flittle ones. They felt absolutely
OL,15,Ffine, but that's under the assumption
OL,16,Fthat you're putting something in your
OL,17,Fear that actually works.
