OL,6,F"There was the odd occasion when you'd
OL,7,Fhear a noise and you'd think 'that's
OL,8,Fpretty loud'... but you use what
OL,9,Fyou're supplied."
OL,11,FHe started experiencing tinnitus while
OL,12,Fhe was still serving, but it wasn't
OL,13,Funtil he left the military that he got
OL,14,Fhis hearing looked at.
