OL,6,F"I was increasingly starting to
OL,7,Fstruggle in social settings, in
OL,8,Fconversations and in busy places. I
OL,9,Fsuspected that my hearing had taken a
OL,10,Fbit of a knock, so I went and had it
OL,11,Fchecked out, and they confirmed there
OL,12,Fwas a fair amount of hearing loss in
OL,13,Fmy left ear."
OL,15,FHe was given a hearing aid, but finds
OL,16,Fit uncomfortable due to the amount of
OL,17,Fbackground noise it picks up.
