OL,6,FMr Stone added: "I'm back at square
OL,7,Fone. It's very difficult to keep track
OL,8,Fof who's saying what, particularly in
OL,9,Flarge settings.
OL,11,F"Generally, I tend to find that I
OL,12,Fexclude myself from big conversations,
OL,13,Fand I'd rather go off and chat with
OL,14,Fsomeone one-on-one. Or, the
OL,15,Falternative is to pretend you've heard
OL,16,Fwhat's been said, go along with it and
OL,17,Fthen walk away completely oblivious."
OL,19,FDavid Pettifer, who also served in the
OL,20,FRoyal Marines, says British servicemen
OL,21,Fand women "deserved better".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
