OL,6,FThe veteran, from Birmingham, said:
OL,7,F"It's a huge disappointment to know
OL,8,Fthat a massive conglomerate like 3M,
OL,9,Fwho were obligated to supply soldiers
OL,10,Fwith quality equipment which worked
OL,11,Fproperly, were willing to put profit
OL,12,Fover the welfare of individuals who
OL,13,Fstep up to serve their country.
OL,15,F"I think I can speak for all British
OL,16,Fservicemen and women who have been
OL,17,Faffected by this betrayal when I say
OL,18,Fthat we deserved a lot better."
