OL,6,FMr Pettifer worked with the heavy
OL,7,Fweapons and anti-tank sub-unit between
OL,8,F2002 and 2012, completing three tours
OL,9,Fin Afghanistan.
OL,11,FThe 47-year-old added: "My hearing
OL,12,Floss affects me on a daily basis, even
OL,13,Fto the point where my wife has to keep
OL,14,Frepeating things when I mishear.
OL,16,F"In other instances, including in the
OL,17,Fwork I've done since leaving the
OL,18,FMarines, I have often felt embarrassed
OL,19,Fwhen I've had to ask people to repeat
OL,20,Fthemselves after not hearing them
OL,21,Fcorrectly."
