OL,6,FKP Law is encouraging people to come
OL,7,Fforward if they think they might have
OL,8,Fbeen affected by the ear defenders.
OL,10,FMr Longstaff said: "One of the British
OL,11,Fmilitary's core values is integrity.
OL,12,FBy supplying earplugs they knew were
OL,13,Fdefective, 3M showed no integrity.
OL,15,F"It is only right that the men and
OL,16,Fwomen whose lives have been impacted
OL,17,Freceive justice and compensation."
OL,19,FThe Ministry of Defence says it would
OL,20,Fnot comment on ongoing legal
OL,21,Fproceedings.
